my.xkb script maps keys for EN and RU language pairs in the following way:

SPACE -> CAPS
Level3 mod -> SPACE
Space+j -> Left 
Space+l -> Right 
Space+i -> Up
Space+k -> Down 
Space+h -> BackSpace
Space+; -> Del 

put script in $HOME/.config/xkb/symbols and activate it with:

xkbcomp $HOME/.config/xkb/symbols/my $DISPLAY
